properties.description: Maggie's Farm is a very small family grower of quality raspberries that are sold to fine restaurants in nearby Madison.  We do not register ourselves as organic.  Our customers trust that we do not apply chemicals of any kind to our raspberries.  They are big and bountiful and naturally raised.
